data.meta_description: Civil War Union Army Officer. He entered the Union Army as a Private in Company H, 19th Pennsylvania Volunteer Infantry. He served with his unit through it's three month enlistment, and was honorably mustered out on August 29, 1861. On September 11, 1861 he secured an appointed as a Captain in the newly raised 69th...
